title: Gallery | Gunners get ready for Liverpool
body_text:
A clash with Liverpool in the Barclays Women's Super League approaches and our Gunners were hard at work at London Colney in preparation.
Fresh from her return on Wednesday evening, Leah Williamson was back in training with the squad and Laura Wienroither continued her ACL recovery by participating in the team warm-up.
